{
  "abilities": "",
  "character_name": "林路",
  "character_schedule": {
    "afternoon": "打羽毛球，逛文创店。",
    "day": 6,
    "evening": "和朋友吃火锅，聊起在写的小说和曾经的天才少女嫁做人妇，唏嘘不已。回家后联系天才少女，天才少女抱怨生活不幸福，很难过，想劝她离婚。",
    "morning": "",
    "night": "",
    "noon": "自然醒，自己做饭，做出黑暗料理，水饺全烂。打游戏。"
  },
  "comments": [
    {
      "author": "123",
      "text": "他和我说了，因为时代的变化，思想的进步，所以他对过去喜爱的作品也会有新的看法，处于批评和继续喜欢之间，我感觉到他也是一个思想信徒的人，我也会跟他分享我。生命中新的进步的思想，而不是我们只讨论很保守的，很安全的观点。",
      "timestamp": "2026/3/12 00:26:35"
    }
  ],
  "completed": false,
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "content": "中午好~",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:45",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "看到雪了吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "又是做了失败料理的一天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "【领结小猫心碎】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "12:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "aiyaaaaaaa",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:21",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "我忙着呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "在看雪",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "今天的雪好漂亮啊！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯！",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "吃午饭了吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯吃了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "在山下面馆吃了面条",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们自己还带了很多零食上来",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "有带喝茶的茶具吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "或者你们的是或者你们去的山上有凉亭吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "有啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么突然说这个？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯这种天气坐在凉亭里面看雪喝茶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "很惬意自在",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "“晚来天欲雪，能饮一杯无？”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "“能”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是古风小生啊？啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "【在下不才未得姑娘青睐古风小生表情包】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "我喜欢在看雪的时候喝茶，我是古风小生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "【ok】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "茶没有，东方树叶可不可以？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不错啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "至少有茶味hhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "山上的树枝都落满了雪吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我的脑袋里面一片空白，想不出华丽的形容词",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "那就不要想了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我这么多年学的诗词歌赋都不都白费了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "让我来想好了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "好久没有看到南方的雪了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "北方的雪苍茫浑厚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "会让我想起 穷阴连晦朔，积雪满山川",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "你别这么搞，你显得我很文盲",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "没事",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "中国人讲究的以景寓情，以情于景",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "心里想什么就说什么就好了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "哪怕看到雪说好白好大也ok啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我还没有这么问吗？我至少能说得出天地白茫茫一片",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "恭喜你",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "初步达到了曹雪芹的水平",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "啥意思？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "我读书少，你别骗我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "好一似食尽鸟投林，落了片白茫茫大地真干净",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "这和你说的也差不多意思",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "我发现你为了哄我，什么鬼话都说得出口",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "我我不会为了哄你，委屈自己的专业",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我相信曹雪芹也不是一看到天地间一片大雪时马上就想到了这么凄美的诗词",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "同根同源",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想起有年和我的表弟去旅行，途经黄河好吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "我表弟现在也是中文系的研究生，他看到黄河第一反应也是啊，好黄的水",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "可是作为一个中国人，学了那么多年语文",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "看到美景总想说点什么了不起的话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "我来说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "微风摇庭树，细雪下帘隙。\n萦空如雾转，凝阶似花积。\n不见杨柳春，徒见桂枝白。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们南方的雪下的不大，只是薄薄的覆盖一层树梢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "阶梯上是残雪未消，远山的积雪也不会太厚重",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "比较配这首诗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "这首感觉好冷门啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "我没学过。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "我记得这首诗是没有出现在浙教版的教材里面",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "看来也没有选入你们江苏的教材",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "你说到这个我想起一句诗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "也不知道能不能算是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "崇祯14年，整个爱尔兰都在下雪。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "前段时间网上这句话非常火",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，我也有刷到",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "我很多学生还在朋友圈转了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "你们也觉得这诗写得很有意境吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得这个诗写的其实挺乱七八糟的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是读起来有种说不出来的感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "很上头",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是从中感受到了苍凉？苍茫之类的感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "对",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "但是这首诗又是那种拼拼凑凑的网络名句，所以我不知道有这种感觉，对不对？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "不要怀疑你的任何感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "你从一个诗词里面，那就是什么，那就是什么",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "能从这句里面感受到苍凉孤独太正常了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也能感觉到啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为他把夏雪和离我们非常遥远的大时代关联到了一起",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:48"
    },
    {
      "content": "又有现代和古代的冲突，崇祯第一反应会让人想到传统的沉闷的古代，可是爱尔兰又会给人感觉很现代",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "有冲突，有矛盾，有时代感，空间感",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "所以会让我们有空旷沧桑之感，甚至还会有点悲伤和孤独",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:49"
    },
    {
      "content": "对对对，我也是这种感觉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "好果然还得是你们专业的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我看到网上有很多人在骂这句，说啥也不是",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:50"
    },
    {
      "content": "确实不大能算作一句诗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "但排放现代诗来看的话，现代诗创作的体裁相对自由",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "说是诗也无妨",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:51"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么你们学文学都是两头讨好，两头都不得罪？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhh个人审美的事情没什么，非要分个高低吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "不说这个了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:52"
    },
    {
      "content": "你要看雪到什么时候？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "我天黑之前下山吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "4点多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:53"
    },
    {
      "content": "好，注意安全",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "你和朋友一起去的吧，那你快跟他玩吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "一直抱着手机，等会他该抱怨了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:54"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有，他也一直在和人聊天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "你们山上还能看到鸟吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:55"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚看到一只鸟飞过去了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "但我认不出是什么鸟",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "14:56"
    },
    {
      "content": "今天人多吗",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "还好吧不多",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "14:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "我一路上就看到了三个",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
