      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:57"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚才和高中的同学吃完饭 聊了好多高中时候的事情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "回想起高中的时候，我们有个女同学很聪明，很优秀，很有才华好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "曾经，她的梦想是读中文系，成为一名优秀的作家",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:58"
    },
    {
      "content": "干嘛突然和我聊你的白月光？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "23:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "几个意思啊你？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "不是白月光，就是同学而已",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "23:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "单纯的同学",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "我对他没有任何男女的感情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "只有欣赏。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:00"
    },
    {
      "content": "好了，好了，别解释了，解释那么多干嘛？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我怕你不信我",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "我信不信你这重要吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:01"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯重要啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "【小猫点头】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "你是不是不大开心了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:02"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，所以你闭嘴",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "懒得听你回忆你和天才女同学的高中时代",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我更应该说完了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:03"
    },
    {
      "content": "说完你就知道不是让你生气的事，不要误会",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "没有说误会",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "你别自作多情好吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:04"
    },
    {
      "content": "好，你没有误会",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "是我自作多情，想太多了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "总之后来这位女同学没有读中文系",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:05"
    },
    {
      "content": "高考志愿被父母篡改成了会计",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "后来他留校考研，考上了中文系研究生",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "可是父亲以死相逼，让他回去嫁人了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:06"
    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "神经",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "跟我搁这拍电视剧呢，还以死相逼",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:07"
    },
    {
      "content": "都什么年代了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你同学才20来岁吧，那么着急嫁人吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "据说他是从小村庄出来的，具体家庭情况我不清楚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:08"
    },
    {
      "content": "好像是吧。妈给他找到了家庭条件比较好的男生，着急让他去结婚吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "总之从那之后他就消失了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也没有他的微信，只有他的班级群，他再也没有在高中班级群发过消息",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:09"
    },
    {
      "content": "嫁人了，又不是失踪了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "怎么会一点消息都没有啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "嫁过去的家庭正常吗？别最后演变成什么凶案了，给我来这个大反转",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:10"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我受不了啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "大晚上别和我讲这些惊悚的东西",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "倒也不是这个走向...",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:11"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚才和老同学吃饭，从老同学那里听来，这个女孩三生二胎了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "据说老公虽然有钱，但是素质很低",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "在外面花天酒地",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "这个女同学在被查出二胎之前在写小说，已经联系出版社了，很有可能出版",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为二胎这个计划也被打断了，家里人说电脑有辐射，把她的电脑也扔了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "???",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "这不神经吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "纯纯神经",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "有病啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "这还不离婚，在干吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也不知道啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "可能她有自己的难处吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "我们外人无从得知",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你是怎么知道这事的？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "老同学的女朋友是她高中的闺蜜",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "本来嫁了人后就不怎么联系了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为写作被阻止的事情，找到了曾经的闺蜜倾诉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "闺蜜转述：她好像距离梦想太远了，再也看不见了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "【小狗痛哭】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊啊啊啊啊啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "为什么这样？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:18"
    },
    {
      "content": "为什么要这样毁掉一个有梦想的女孩？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "家庭到底给人带来了什么？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "唉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:19"
    },
    {
      "content": "想到和你说是因为你也会让我觉得你有梦想，有想做的 事情，想看到的天地",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "我希望你不要有天被世俗的规矩淹没了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你放心",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:20"
    },
    {
      "content": "我根本没有这位女同学的才华",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "别说出了，我连工作总结这周都没写好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "才华又不止于写作",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:21"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的心气，你想要的，你渴望的，我都希望它们被世俗阻挠",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "借你吉言吧",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "我现在还迷茫得很",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:22"
    },
    {
      "content": "20多岁正是迷茫的时候。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "有时想想真的很奇怪啊，大部分人毕业是22岁",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "刚一离开校园就被贴上了社会人的身份",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:23"
    },
    {
      "content": "要去面对很多学校里根本没教过的事情",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "连这些部分都还没有学好，可能要去面对结婚生育的挑战",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "还不允许人说不和抱怨。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:24"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为在社会规则里面，我们已经是社会人了，已经是大人",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "唉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "你别说这些让人emo的话了，好不好？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:25"
    },
    {
      "content": "道理都懂，我也都明白",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "但又有什么办法呢？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "有",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:26"
    },
    {
      "content": "我觉得至少有一个办法不会让人太糟糕",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "那就是没有满足自己非常渴望，自己的心里度成熟之外的这两个条件",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "绝对不要结婚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:27"
    },
    {
      "content": "【举牌快跑】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊，所以你特地和我说这一通就是为了叫我不要结婚？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "【听泉做笔记】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:28"
    },
    {
      "content": "是没有满足这两个条件的时候，不要结婚",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "我又不是无缘无故的反婚反育",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "要是有人的梦想就是结婚，并且他也能够在家庭中找到幸福，维持幸福。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:29"
    },
    {
      "content": "轮得到我反对这些金童玉女吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊，那你意思是说我没有在家庭中获得幸福的能力了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "我找茬都想不到你这个角度",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:30"
    },
    {
      "content": "你才25诶",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "其实还是小朋友",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "那你也才二十七啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:31"
    },
    {
      "content": "是啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "我也没觉得自己是成熟的大人啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "懂了，男人至死是少年是吧？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:32"
    },
    {
      "content": "【咯噔一下】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "【别搞我了，大小姐】",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "就是因为你聊天的时候经常跟我说你好迷茫",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:33"
    },
    {
      "content": "迷茫的时候不适合做任何重大决定",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "我知道的",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:34"
    },
    {
      "content": "我还没有做好任何准备。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "主要我不觉得自己有能力养小孩",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "一个月挣那三瓜两枣的都不够给小孩买尿布呢",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:35"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "我之前听播客时，听到一个生育学的专家说",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "生育率低的解决办法就是国家给每个生孩子的家庭发100万的补助",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:36"
    },
    {
      "content": "金额只能往上走，不能减少",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "补助到位，生育率就绝不是问题",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:37"
    },
    {
      "content": "专家总算是说了一句人话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "给我笑死了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "播客的主持人就问专家，那你这个想法有得到过什么专业人士的赞同吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:38"
    },
    {
      "content": "专家说我没跟专业人士提过，我知道，不会有人赞成的，100万不可能",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "hhhhhh",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "笑死我了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:39"
    },
    {
      "content": "快一点了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "你困不困？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:40"
    },
    {
      "content": "那我最后再说一句",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "不要担心以后的日子艰难",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "先活下去，最现实的缺钱的困难一定会被我们活下去打败",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:41"
    },
    {
      "content": "本来是有些困了。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "给你这个毒鸡汤一下整精神了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "你倒是说说我以后怎么解决这个问题，我会人到中年忽然变富吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:42"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "乍富只能交给彩票",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "我想说的是，长大可能需要很长时间的积累",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:43"
    },
    {
      "content": "在30岁之前想拥有面对现实困难的能力有点难",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "等等吧，或许到了那一天，问题还不能化解，但是自己的心已经不一样了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "你的意思好像是解决不了问题就解决制造问题的人？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:44"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "又是我表达不畅吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "马东：“被误解是表达的宿命。”",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:45"
    },
    {
      "content": "我是想说现在会让我焦虑迷茫的那些事情，以后我们都不会怕了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "没关系，你也可以用你自己的理解",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "只是我今天很想说这些话",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:46"
    },
    {
      "content": "辛苦你了，那么晚还听我倾诉",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "00:47"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，我真的很困",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "00:47"
    }
